cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV. 

This paper involves learning to follow natural language instructions by jointly reasoning with visual observations and language inputs, which falls under the intersection of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method also involves reinforcement learning, which is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) research. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.LG, followed by cs.RO and cs.CV.
